## 4. SESSION LOGGING FORM — MOBILE (CRITICAL PATH)

This is the most important mobile workflow. A counselor logs a session immediately after meeting a student. Every friction point costs real time. Follow these rules exactly.

### 4.1 Form Layout on Mobile

