## 9. WHAT DEGRADES GRACEFULLY vs. WHAT MUST WORK ON MOBILE

| Feature | Mobile Status | Rule |
|---|---|---|
| Session log form | **MUST WORK — critical path** | Full functionality, all inputs, submit. Zero compromise. |
| Incident logging | **MUST WORK** | Full form — type, date, severity, description |
| Dashboard student list | **MUST WORK** | Card list replaces table |
| Student profile view | **MUST WORK** | Stacked single-column layout |
| Charts | **View only** | No period toggles, no interactive controls |
| PDF progress report generation | **Degrades** | Hide button on mobile — "Available on desktop" |
| Organization analytics | **Degrades** | Link to "View full analytics on desktop" |
| Cohort comparison chart | **Degrades** | Hidden below md |
| Success plan builder | **Degrades** | Redirect to desktop — complex multi-step form |
| AI Ask feature | **MUST WORK** | Single textarea + submit — simple enough for mobile |
| AI briefing view (read only) | **MUST WORK** | Scrollable text panel |
| Escalation banner | **MUST WORK** | Full-width alert, always visible, acknowledgment button meets 48px target |
| User account management | **Degrades** | Owner-only, owner is on desktop |

