## 10. EMPTY STATES ON MOBILE

Empty state components must be vertically centered and fit within a single viewport without scrolling.

```tsx
// Mobile empty state — student list (counselor with no assigned students yet)
<div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-8 text-center min-h-[60vh]">
  <div className="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-olive-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
    <Users size={24} className="text-olive-400" aria-hidden="true" />
  </div>
  <h2 className="font-serif text-heading text-olive-900 mb-2">No students assigned yet</h2>
  <p className="font-sans text-body-sm text-olive-500">
    Your administrator will assign students to your caseload.
  </p>
</div>
```

